title: Zanetor Rawlings Organizes Free Health Screening (PHOTO + VIDEO)
text: Dr. Zanetor Rawling, NDC aspirant for Klottey Korle constituency has organized free health screening for people living in her constituency. Hundreds thronged in their numbers to the Latter Day Saints Church in Asylum Dam to have their health checked. They were screened on blood pressure, malaria, breast cancer, sugar levels, eye, but to name a few. According to the 37-year-old daughter of Ex-President Jerry John Rawlings, the free health screening is ‘voluntary social responsibility thing’ with free services from doctors, nurses and pharmacists.
